      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ADHANA PHILLIP (1) impressive winner in quick time last start when scoring by 12 lengths (19.78) at this track. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. EVOLVE (2) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish one length back in third (20.07) at this track in a TG1-4W over 342m. Leading player again. LIFE'S A JOKE (5) was below best last time finishing fifth at this track, but prior to that had been racing well including a TG1-4W win two back at this track. Can feature with the right run. MAFIA MISTRESS (4) was well supported last time but could only manage second (20.18), beaten 2.5 lengths. Won at her only start from this box. Well placed and gets her chance.",
